ns0:simpleDc.ns2:title: Norton Bay Inter-Tribal Watershed Council - Tubuktulik River
ns0:simpleDc.ns2:subject: Tubuktulik River general field form
Elim, Alaska

ns0:dcTerms.ns2:abstract: Background information and data collected from the Tubuktulik River for a watershed program managed by NBITWC. Data from the project included here is compiled into a variety of formats, including onto general field forms, discharge measurement notes and forms, reports and tables with laboratory analytic results, and spreadsheets with site-specific pressure, temperature, and water surface levels. Parameters possibly collected on general field forms include water chemistry from Chemetrics Kit or Hanna Meter, water depth, river depth, river speed, and insects.
